# Our project i.e Covi-Relief would help people in knowing about Covid-19 i.e how it spreads, what precautions should a person take.
# The user would also be able to take a Self-assessment test based on their symptoms and their travel history in the last 14 days.
# Users would also get a feature of registering themselves for the covid vaccine slots so that no rush would be there at vaccination centers.
# It would also show the availability of hospital beds.
